COURT. Q. Do you receive from some of your correspondents goods without advice? A. No; I never did in my life from anybody, without I had some advice of them - I did not receive two bags within a week of the time these were sent without any advice - I have not received any thing from Mr. Lupton this year - I think I did in December - he sent the wool down, and it laid there a week - he then sent me advice that if I liked it at a certain price, I might keep it.(
